    "7226314": {
        "Desc": "Report your intel to Momoyo",
        "Step": "All three Fatui spies have provided you with important intelligence concerning the impostor Gendou Ringo. Head back to the safehouse and inform Momoyo.",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Momoyo",
                    "T": "Well, you're finally back. Did you manage to get any intel from them?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "???",
                    "T": "You tell Momoyo the details of the intelligence you got from the Fatui."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Momoyo",
                    "T": "Hmph. Seriously, between the two of you talking over each other, your report was as clear as mud. But don't worry, I got the gist of it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Momoyo",
                    "T": "So, the fake at the shrine is named Lyudochka. Her superior has actually been pushing her to make further contact with you, but for some reason, she hasn't acted yet."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Momoyo",
                    "T": "As such, this superior, whom they call \"the Teacher,\" is going to give her a new assignment tonight. She will have to leave the shrine and go to Watatsumi Island."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "That's exactly how it is, yes."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Momoyo",
                    "T": "The details of this operation in Watatsumi Island is key intelligence. We must find some way to get our hands on it."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But we don't know where they're going to meet up..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "We could follow her from the shrine."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Momoyo",
                    "T": "That is so. But given that the area near the Grand Narukami Shrine is filled with mountain paths, we're quite likely to lose her."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Momoyo",
                    "T": "Wait just a moment."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Momoyo",
                    "T": "Here. Use this."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Eh? Isn't this one of those Bamboo Slips you get from the Fortune Slip Box?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Momoyo",
                    "T": "This is no ordinary Bamboo Slip. I've scattered some Shuumatsuban-made elemental powder on it. You can use Elemental Sight to see the traces left by the powder."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh, Paimon gets it now. We'll pretend to draw a Bamboo Slip, and then take the opportunity to get the powder onto her. Hehe, leave it to Paimon!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Momoyo",
                    "T": "Stop waving that slip around! How are you supposed to identify the right target if that powder gets onto you as well, huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "S—Sorry! Paimon's sorry!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Momoyo",
                    "T": "Hmph. Anyway, this powder is somewhat toxic, so fiddle with it willy-nilly at your own risk."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "#(Y'know, {NICKNAME}, Momoyo seems really fierce, but she's actually a pretty nice person...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Momoyo",
                    "T": "Hey! Less jibber-jabber, more work! Any further delay and the sun's going to go down!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Alright, we're going, we're going!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
